The '''Hunting expert''' can be found in the [[Feldip Hunter area]]. She resides in a hut marked with a [[File:Lumbridge Guide icon.png]] on the world map. There are [[Feldip Hunter area#Travel|several ways]] to get there. She will sell the [[Hunter cape]] for 99,000 [[coins]] to players who have 99 [[Hunter]].

The clothing she is wearing is [[larupia hunter gear|larupia clothing]], commonly worn by hunters in her area. The Hunting expert is one out of the few [[Cape of Accomplishment]] sellers who do not have a specific name. (The others being the [[Estate Agent]], [[Master Fisher]], [[Head chef]] and [[Master Crafter]]).

She is one of only three female NPCs that sells a cape of accomplishment, the other being [[Surgeon General Tafani]] and [[Twiggy O'Korn]].

==Stock==
Note: If a player has multiple [[Skill mastery|99s]], they will receive the trimmed variant of the cape instead.
